{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM07_010.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x24,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I've written so much into this reference book. It's almost full."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It just goes to show how many items you've Synthesized. I'll have a look at the recipe."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Did you remember anything?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, I've remembered something that will be good news for you... The location of the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat!? R-really!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes, there's no mistake. The \"Cauldron of Knowledge\" is located at a place called the \"Gates of Wisdom\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "The \"Gates of Wisdom\"... So if I go there, I'd be able to get the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\"?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "If I have the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\", I'd be able to use even more amazing alchemy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "And maybe it'll make all of your memories come back at once!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Sophie..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "However, at this time, it's impossible to reach the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That's because the path to the \"Gates of Wisdom\" requires a key to open."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "A key...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Wait, you're the one who made the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\", right? Why did you lock it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...Because with the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\", anyone would be able to use alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I told you before, the power of alchemy is enormous. Misusing it could result in disaster."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "That's why I decided to seal away the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\", until someone worthy of using it appeared."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Yes, however... It seems such a person has finally appeared before me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "...Sophie. I'll teach you the way to make the key."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Wait... Is it really okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I believe that you would use the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\" for good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Oh Plachta...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "That said, creating the key will not be easy. Are you still willing to do it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Of course!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I see. In that case, I'll teach you the recipe."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "\"You must add Sun Drops and Eternity Scales to Haze Grass Petals.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "This will create the key to reach the Cauldron... The recipe for the \"Key of Truth\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Uu, I've never heard of any of these materials..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "That's why I told you it wouldn't be easy. Think of it as the final test to reach the Cauldron."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "...Okay! I'll definitely make it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I know that you can do it, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Alright, first I need to research these materials. I should ask a bunch of people."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Plachta told you about a new gathering field that she remembered."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Plachta learned the skill \"<CLGR>Knowledge of All<CLNR>\"."
        }
    ]
}